Downloading:
http://ngspice.sourceforge.net/download.html
(Source:https://sourceforge.net/projects/ngspice/files/ng-spice-rework/34/)
Download and extract it.

To open the ngspice- Go to bin->ngspice.exe

To open a circuit-> first change the directory in ngspice by using cd command.
Commands to run:
source <filename>.cir
run
display
